== Welcome to AppStarter

This small app demonstrate how to create a rails 3.1 web app from scratch and 
support the following features:

1. Sorcery as authentication component 
       
2. Integrate less-rails-bootstrap to support twitter bootstrap as UI framework

3. Simple_form and twitter bootstrap integration

4. CarrierWave to upload image

5. RSpec to do TDD, optionally Cucumber to do BDD